    "data": [
        {
            "title": "OPEC首次展望2027年 預計石油需求穩步成長",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> OPEC對2027年的首次詳細評估預測，全球石油需求將繼續以穩定的速度成長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博新聞社看到的一份OPEC秘書處報告，2027年全球石油消費將增加每日130萬桶，僅僅略低於今年的增幅，日消費量將達到平均1.079億桶。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">OPEC預計的需求增量，大約是該組織預計的其競爭對手供應成長的兩倍，這表明除非該組織繼續恢復產量，否則明年全球市場可能會偏緊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，OPEC過去的需求預測已經被證明過於樂觀。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5d957820-e890-38da-a48c-f262b63a0294-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報告顯示，12月份OPEC+聯盟每天的總產量減少23.8萬桶，降至每日4,283萬桶，主要原因是哈薩克產量下滑。由於哈薩克原油的關鍵出口碼頭遭到襲擊，該國日產量減少23.7萬桶，至每日152萬桶。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題OPEC’s First Look at 2027 Shows Demand Growing at Steady Pace</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/opec%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%9B2027%E5%B9%B4-%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E7%A9%A9%E6%AD%A5%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7-133411231.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 22:25:47",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國抵押貸款利率降至2024年9月以來最低",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:抵押貸款;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/抵押貸款\">抵押貸款</a>利率上周跌至數年來的最低水平之一，引發的一連串購房和再融資活動為低迷的房地產市場帶來希望。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據抵押貸款銀行家協會(MBA)周三發布的數據，截至1月9日當周，30年期抵押貸款的合同利率下降7個基點至6.18%。這是自2024年9月以來的最低水平，也是自2022年以來的最低水平之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鎖定前5年利率的可調利率抵押貸款大幅下降近50個基點，至5.42%，為2023年5月以來的次低水平。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-72a26ea3-f4ff-3d3d-b7c4-e3e8c0d476a4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在住房融資成本下降的背景下，MBA購房指數上周大漲近16%，至2023年2月以來的第二高水平；再融資指標躍升逾40%，為9月以來最大漲幅。抵押貸款活動在歲末年初和臨近假期時出現大幅周波動是常見現象。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管如此，這些數據表明，近年來飽受負擔能力不佳困擾的房地產市場出現一定緩解跡象。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國10月新屋銷售基本持平 此前9月出現成長</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自1990年以來每周開展的該協會調查，匯集了抵押貸款銀行家、商業銀行和儲貸機構的反饋。相關數據覆蓋了美國零售住宅抵押貸款申請總量的75%以上。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Mortgage Rates Slide to One of the Lowest Levels Since 2022</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%BC%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E9%99%8D%E8%87%B32024%E5%B9%B49%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E-125840373.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 21:36:08",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "頂住貿易主義保護壓力 中國鋼材出口創出紀錄新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"頂住貿易主義保護壓力 中國鋼材出口創出紀錄新高\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"662\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VTk4AiMgWJ.HgM6WuNJfZw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/841d54b0-f139-11f0-975f-c27bcc398722\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">頂住貿易主義保護壓力 中國鋼材出口創出紀錄新高</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
