        {
            "title": "泰國高鐵建設中起重機倒塌 砸中火車致27人死亡",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 泰國東北部高速鐵路網建設中使用的一台起重機周三倒塌，正好砸中一列行駛中的火車，造成至少27人死亡，數十人受傷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">呵叻府府尹Anupong Suksomnit對記者表示，救援人員正在切割快速列車損毀的車廂，以收斂至少七具遇難者遺體。他還表示，近80名受傷乘客正在當地醫院接受治療。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據泰國國家鐵路稱，起重機倒塌砸中了從曼谷開往烏汶府列車的兩節車廂，車上載有195名乘客和乘務人員。據當地媒體報導，坍塌事故涉及一台用於吊裝高架高鐵網混凝土梁的起重機，其衝擊力導致車廂脫軌並起火。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-755cab30-64d2-3a65-a660-b51ae3cde76e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"泰國東北部，高鐵起重機倒塌砸中列車來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"1707\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rMn0.i_Je1WrTlnyDcykNQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTE3MDc7Y2Y9d2VicA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5092bcf8e29a2801b06d652342b226d4\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">泰國東北部，高鐵起重機倒塌砸中列車來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">泰國總理阿努廷告訴記者，泰國官員將調查起重機倒塌的原因，並補充說，項目負責人將被追究責任。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該項目建設的主承包商Italian-Thai Development Pcl股價在曼谷股市下跌7.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這個高鐵網絡是中國「一帶一路」倡議的一部分，旨在到2030年通過老撾將泰國與中國連接起來。鐵路線全長609公里，預計耗資約130億美元，將通過一座橫跨湄公河的大橋與老撾-中國鐵路連接。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Thai Crane Collapse on Moving Express Train Kills 27 People (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD%E4%B8%AD%E8%B5%B7%E9%87%8D%E6%A9%9F%E5%80%92%E5%A1%8C-%E7%A0%B8%E4%B8%AD%E7%81%AB%E8%BB%8A%E8%87%B427%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1-080050615.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 16:35:50",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
